   Create your own story, asking the user for different parts of speech to fill in the blanks. If you run into errors, make sure to use Chapter 3's guidance to figure out where the errors are coming from. 

   ~~~~

   noun = input("Enter a noun:")
   print("The", noun, "walked down the street.")